title: Romae Clementia Bracelet
description: The Clementia cuff bracelet is based on an ancient Etruscan example from the seventh century BC. Its strong architectural structure is softened by the gentle waves woven throughout, creating a glistening and unforgettable signature piece that you'll never want to be without.
